<p>The backtest results page enables you to share your backtest results. You need to make a backtest public in order to share it. To make a backtest public, on the backtest results page, click the <span class='tab-name'>Share</span> tab and then click <span class='button-name'>Make Public</span>. Once you make a backtest public, the <span class='tab-name'>Share</span> tab displays a link to the <a href='/docs/v2/cloud-platform/backtesting/report'>backtest report</a>, a link to an embedded backtest result, and a script to embed the embedded backtest result into a website.</p>

<p>The following widget is an example of an embedded backtest result:</p>

<div class='python'><div class="qc-embed-frame python" style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 100%; min-height: 100px; min-width: 300px;"><div class="qc-embed-dummy" style="padding-top: 56.25%;"></div><div class="qc-embed-element" style="position: absolute; top: 0; bottom: 0; left: 0; right: 0;"><iframe class="qc-embed-backtest" src="https://www.quantconnect.com/terminal/processCache?request=embedded_backtest_4659d3886ac40cd512ff32bc4dcb3ec4.html" style="max-width: calc(100vw - 30px); max-height: 100vw; overflow: hidden;" scrolling="no" width="100%" height="100%"></iframe></div></div></div>

