<p>To attach the embedded backtest result to a forum discussion, see <a href="/docs/v2/cloud-platform/community/forum#07-Create-Discussions">Create Discussions</a> or <a href="/docs/v2/cloud-platform/community/forum#08-Post-Comments">Post Comments</a>.</p>

<p>After you've made your backtest results public, the results are always stored, anyone with the link can access the results, and the results can't be made private again because someone may have already cloned your project.</p>
